Dependency
Purpose
spring-context
Spring Core container and dependency injection
spring-orm
Integration of Spring with JPA/Hibernate
spring-jdbc
JDBC support and DataSource utilities
spring-tx
Declarative transaction management
spring-data-jpa
JPA repository support
hibernate-core
JPA implementation (Hibernate)
jakarta.persistence-api
JPA annotations (@Entity, @Id, etc.)
mysql-connector-j
MySQL JDBC driver
slf4j-simple
Console logging



